Job.create(name: '10th Excellence in Teaching Conference',url:'10EITC',tagline:'Enhance your knowledge of best practice in teaching',short:'Stay up to Date on the Latest Developments in Teaching', content: "Are you interested in learning more about best practice in teaching or in building your network in academia? Sign up to attend the 10th Excellence in Teaching Conference on 17th June 2016 at the Strand campus. Dr. Shankutala Banjali from the London School of Economics and Political Science will be delivering the keynote address, followed by a series of masterclasses delivered by the various faculties, panel discussions and lightning talks.")
Job.create(name: 'See a Careers Consultant',url:'SACC',tagline:'Expert, confidential careers guidance for PhDs and Research Staff',short:'Get clarity on your future by talking to one of our expert careers consultants', content: "Thank you for lighting the fire under my feet!’ said one King’s PhD this year, after a conversation with a Careers Consultant.  Whether you’ve a clear idea, some ideas or no idea at all about your future, come and talk with one of us about what happens next.  We act as a confidential and neutral sounding board, provide feedback on application documents and critique your interview performance, whether you’re looking for a career in academia or outside.  Find out more here http://www.kcl.ac.uk/campuslife/services/careers/Researchers/Careers-advice-for-PhD-students.aspx, or call 020 7848 7134 or email careers@kcl.ac.uk for a one:one appointment across all King’s campuses, phone or Skype.")